PATCH http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/announcements/{announcement_id}/pin
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "is_pinned": true
}

###

### Delete Announcement
DELETE http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/announcements/{announcement_id}
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

