# ----------------------------------------
# Tenant Chat (REST fallback for WebSocket)
# ----------------------------------------

### Get Chat History
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/chat/messages?limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}

###

### Get Chat History (before specific message)
GET http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/chat/messages?before_id={message_id}&limit=50
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}

###

### Send Chat Message (REST fallback)
POST http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/chat/messages
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "content": "Hello everyone!"
}

###

### Edit Chat Message
PATCH http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/chat/messages/{message_id}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

{
  "content": "Hello everyone! (edited)"
}

###

### Delete Chat Message
DELETE http://localhost:8080/v1/tenants/{tenant_id}/chat/messages/{message_id}
Authorization: Bearer {access_token}
Idempotency-Key: {{$guid}}

